International Hat Company


Former International Hat warehouse (1954–1976) in Soulard, St. Louis, Missouri.[1] The building was originally built in 1904 by Brown Shoe Company.[1] Since 1980, it has been used as a senior and disabled living facility.[1] The building is listed with the National Register of Historic Places.[1][2]




