About
Dr. Frank Pellegrino, MD is a Doctor primarily located in Clermont, FL, with another office in Leesburg, FL. He has 29 years of experience. His specialties include Family Medicine.                    Dr. Pellegrino is affiliated with                            Villages Regional Hospital,                            Villiages Regional Hospital and                            Leesburg Regional Medical Center.
